    Class defines an access type to the node source for the administration and utilization. When a node source is created user specifies this access level. Supported levels ME designates the creator identity ALL designates all users identity users=user1,use2;groups=group1,group2 designates specific users and groups Deprecated levels MY_GROUPS designates all groups of creator PROVIDER designate the identity of node provider (the one who added the node to the node source can use it) PROVIDER_GROUPS designate all groups of node provider (only people from these groups will have an access to the node)
